  "body": "# Components\r\n\r\n## Continuous Integration Visibility\r\n\r\n* :sparkles: Add Java 26 support to CI Visibility (#10929 - @daniel-mohedano)\r\n\r\n## Profiling\r\n\r\n* :sparkles: Update Java profiler library to 1.40.0 (#10932 - @jbachorik)\r\n  * [Java 26 compatibility fix](https://github.com/DataDog/java-profiler/pull/428)\r\n  * [Improve stackwalking performance](https://github.com/DataDog/java-profiler/pull/423)\r\n\r\n# Instrumentations\r\n\r\n## RMI\r\n\r\n* :bug::closed_lock_with_key: Use primitive types for RMI context payload serialization (#10937 - @PerfectSlayer)\r\n\r\n",
